    <abstract>
      <t>   The updates to RFC 5280 described in this document provide alignment
   with the 2013 specification for the X.509 Internet Public Key
   Infrastructure Online Certificate Status Protocol-OCSP [RFC6960], and
   add support for Certificate Transparency [RFC6962].

